    "display_name": "Born This Way",
    "long_instructions": "### Born This Way\r\n\r\n**Define:** *Born This Way* by Lady Gaga is known for its pulsing synth leads and powerful drum beats. Your challenge is to create a remix that highlights these features using only the synth lead and beat tracks from the song.\r\n\r\n**Prepare:** Explore the synth lead and beat tracks from the song. Plan how you'll combine different beats and leads to create a strong, energetic sound. Listen to the example below to hear what this could sound like.\r\n\r\n**Try:** Use at least 3 different beat tracks and 2 different synth lead tracks. Organize your code using 2 functions. Add at least one effect to shape the sound and create energy in your remix.\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#ebe8f1; border: 0; border-radius: 10px; clear:both; padding: 5px\">\r\n\r\nNeed some help? Try the [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i> Docs](#clickable=documentation-button) in the upper-right corner!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n**Reflect:** Does your remix capture the pulse and power of the original song? How did your use of functions and effects help shape the final sound? In order to complete this level, your remix must include:\r\n\r\n- 3 different beat tracks\r\n- 2 different lead tracks\r\n- 2 functions\r\n- At least 1 effect",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Born This Way by Lada Gaga is filled with pulsing synth leads and full drum beats. Create a remix of the song that emphasizes these qualities.",
    "thumbnail_url": "https://curriculum.code.org/media/musiclab/library-launch2024/packs/lady_gaga_born_this_way/lady_gaga_born_this_way.jpg",
